      • setTransfoFromGCP

        public abstract void setTransfoFromGCP()
        Abstract method to compute the parameters of the transformation using the ground control points. The methods of computation differ according to the implementation. Sets the parameters and residuals attributes of class transformation according to the results of this computation.
